er Pekora Usada 后首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上<a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-became-the-most-watched-female-streamer-in-2023/">，成为 2023 年观看次数最多的女性主播</a>。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-became-the-most-watched-female-streamer-in-2023/feed/ 0 110635
 Hololive YouTube官方频道总浏览量在VTuber行业史上首次突破10亿https://p2y.jp/hololive-official-youtube-channel-achieved-1-billion-plays-for-the-first-time-in-vtuber-industry/ https://p2y.jp/hololive-official-youtube-channel-achieved-1-billion-plays-for-the-first-time-in-vtuber-industry/#respondp2y_admin Wed, 03 Jan 2024 03:23:18 +0000 VTuberバーチャルYouTubeYouTuberバーチャルYouTuberホロライブホロライブプロダクション動画総再生数(YouTube) https://p2y.jp/?p=110555 <p> VTuber Office Hololive Production 旗下日本女团 Hololive 官方 YouTube 频道“hololive Hololive – VTuber Group”将于 2024 年发布 […]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-official-youtube-channel-achieved-1-billion-plays-for-the-first-time-in-vtuber-industry/">Hololive官方YouTube频道在VTuber行业历史上首次突破10亿次总浏览量，</a>首发于<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; <p></p><p> VTuber事务所Hololive Productions旗下的日本女子组合Hololive的官方YouTube频道“ <strong>hololive – VTuber Group</strong> ”<strong>截至2024年1月1日（元旦）总计约10亿次视频浏览量158次，观看次数为3,034次</strong>，成为VTuber行业历史上第一个播放量达到10亿次的。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1100" height="619" data-attachment-id="110570" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/hololive-official-youtube-channel-achieved-1-billion-plays-for-the-first-time-in-vtuber-industry/hololive_official_youtube_channel_achieved_1_billion_plays_for_the_first_time_in_vtuber_industry/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/hololive_official_youtube_channel_achieved_1_billion_plays_for_the_first_time_in_vtuber_industry.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="ホロライブ公式YouTubeチャンネル VTuber業界史上初の総再生数10億回を達成" data-image-description="&lt;p>;ホロライブ公式YouTubeチャンネル VTuber業界史上初の総再生数10億回を達成&lt;/p>;
" data-image-caption="&lt;p>;ホロライブ公式YouTubeチャンネル VTuber業界史上初の総再生数10億回を達成&lt;/p>;
" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/hololive_official_youtube_channel_achieved_1_billion_plays_for_the_first_time_in_vtuber_industry.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/hololive_official_youtube_channel_achieved_1_billion_plays_for_the_first_time_in_vtuber_industry.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/hololive_official_youtube_channel_achieved_1_billion_plays_for_the_first_time_in_vtuber_industry.png?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-110570" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>总观看次数突破10亿次的成绩得益于自2023年12月31日（令和5年）（除夕夜）起播出的年末新年特别节目《游游Holo Kuru Holo 2023▷2024~》和《hololive Production》。 COUNTDOWN LIVE 2023▷2024 -hololive side-》存档视频播放数录得特别高的增长。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="年末 Hololive ～Yuku Holo Kuru Holo 2023▷2024～ [#Yuku Holo Kuru Holo 2023]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/p2jx9H5Ck74?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p>此外，两档节目的同时观看人数（观看人数）也较去年大幅增加，其中《hololive Production COUNTDOWN LIVE 2023▷2024 -hololive side-》将成为观看人数最多的节目。 202326 VTuber 共记录 8,222 人。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="Hololive Production COUNTDOWN LIVE 2023▷2024 -hololive side-" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DzP0jXgOC4I?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-